{"tid":1329102,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一名中立球迷對意甲來年排名預測","createTime":"2019-07-18T06:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T11:22:34.000Z","uid":216975,"like":9,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"170d93d102ba15aeab511d66c5558e2b4ce3092d","tid":1329102,"uid":216975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:09:41.000Z","msg":"冠軍-就一定羅馬對祖雲達斯<br />\n第34名-拿玻璃同大國際<br />\n米蘭-傻閪隊<br />\n<br />\n我地祖雲達斯要現實意甲一百連霸<br />\n又陣容大幅補強<br />\n不過獨惧羅馬<br />\n始終羅馬賣哂d主力同勁既人<br />\n隻隻人我都吾識 但係依個先係佢得人驚既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一隊傳統強隊居然夠膽咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />擺空城計<br />\n分分鐘用依支生面口既軍隊殺到我地蛆雲達斯一頸血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e849db5b0dc6585288616a6baea36464a14f9dd","tid":1329102,"uid":555,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:10:58.000Z","msg":"垃圾羅馬算數啦"},{"pid":"26043b5e4157daecc51ca0fc79b4b050a0f0199a","tid":1329102,"uid":3454,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:12:49.000Z","msg":"降班喇羅馬"},{"pid":"8ec8e8708972a6c0a185685b7b1539db29bcf432","tid":1329102,"uid":5649,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:13:34.000Z","msg":"羅馬降班啦，無能用"},{"pid":"9cb50b8249c77bc1037ba316cecfc2135e46dd33","tid":1329102,"uid":216975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e849db5b0dc6585288616a6baea36464a14f9dd","tid":1329102,"uid":555,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:10:58.000Z","msg":"垃圾羅馬算數啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfea8e511cd45e3d6625ab96d8a8d20abfd790a","tid":1329102,"uid":10702,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:49: